request.description:
For every data center in the cross DC setup, the below object should be configured
Issue GET /dataspace for the data center and obtain its nodeName and substitute below
```
{
  "ring": [
    {
      "nodeName": "<substitute the nodeName value obtained from GET <data_center_1>/dataspace>",
      "host": "<domain_of_data_center_1>",
      "port": {{crossdc_port}}
    },
    {
      "nodeName": "<substitute the nodeName value obtained from GET <data_center_2>/dataspace>",
      "host": "<domain_of_data_center_2>",
      "port": {{crossdc_port}}
    }
  ]
}
```
